Backlight
---------

You can use the following commands to turn on / turn off the backlight:

* Turn on backlight:
    .. code-block:: bash

        echo 1 > /sys/class/backlight/panel-lvds-backlight/brightness

* Turn off backlight (screen goes black):
    .. code-block:: bash

        echo 0 > /sys/class/backlight/panel-lvds-backlight/brightness

:pagebreak:`True`